Record Deleted In Table cms_page Id in Table 527 updated keys {"page_id":"527","parent_id":"0","submenu":"0","page_name":"Book Chapter","heading":"Book Chapter","page_slug":"book-chapter","short_description":"","section1":"
The Electronics and Communication Engineering Department aims to be a renowned centre of excellence known for its cutting-edge research, innovative curriculum, and industry-academia partnerships.

Our ultimate goal is to be a beacon of innovation and a catalyst for positive change in the field of Electronics and Communication Engineering. Our vision includes leading breakthroughs in emerging technologies, fostering a culture of diversity and inclusion, and providing global outreach opportunities for students and faculty. With all these developments, the Electronics department has taken a step forward toward establishing the first 5G Lab in the region thus we can say that the department has established itself as a leader in the field.

By prioritizing student success through continuous mentorship and career support, we aim to produce well-groomed professionals equipped with the skills and knowledge to thrive in the rapidly evolving tech industry. The department offers UG in Electronics and Communication Engineering and VLSI, Department also offers a PG program in VLSI Design. The students are trained and certified for Coursera certification courses apart from the academic curriculum.

Vision

To be a renowned Center of Excellence in Electronics and Communication Engineering, developing globally competent ethical resources to serve society.

Mission

  • To impart a robust teaching and learning process thriving on qualified, trained resources and state-of-the-art infrastructure.
  • To promote innovation and research culture by providing students with hands-on experience for solving real-time problems and developing sustainable products and solutions.
  • To imbibe ethical values, entrepreneurial zeal, and lifelong learning ability to develop future-ready professionals.

Highlights

  • Industry tie-ups with Capgemini for 5G Mobile Wireless Communication.
  • Tie-up with Coursera to improve the global competencies of faculty members and students.
  • Students are motivated to do many projects in the laboratories from the second year onwards.
  • Experimental-oriented teaching as per industrial requirements.
  • Special classes on advanced topics.
  • Industry-supported laboratories for VLSI and Telecommunication.
  • Use of audio-visual aids during class.
  • PPT of each course with all the details of the curriculum and the learning objectives.

Record Deleted In Table cms_page Id in Table 548 updated keys {"page_id":"548","parent_id":"0","submenu":"0","page_name":"HoD Message","heading":"HoD Message","page_slug":"hod-message","short_description":"

Elevating Excellence in Computer
Science & Engineering

","section1":"

Dear Students and Future Innovators in Computer Science and Engineering,

I trust this message finds you in excellent health and high spirits. I am Professor Kumud Saxena, honoured to lead the Computer Science and Engineering Department. It is my privilege to extend a warm welcome to our vibrant and dynamic department, where the realm of Computer Science and Engineering is brimming with limitless possibilities.

In the world of Computer Science and Engineering (CSE), diversity and growth serve as our guiding principles. Our CSE professionals are genuine pioneers, navigating through various specializations as their interests and expertise evolve. With our forward-thinking, career focused CSE degree, you are stepping into a world of boundless opportunities. You can immerse yourself in software development, master the craft of computer programming, analyse businesses with precision as a business analyst, sculpt data models to unveil hidden insights, orchestrate the symphony of systems integration, and even take the helm of network management. The canvas is vast, and you are the artist of your journey.

As we march forward into the future, knowledge-based industries take the spotlight, and a nation's prowess is intricately woven with its adept utilization of information technology. Globally, India has emerged as a beacon, offering limitless opportunities in software development and IT-enabled services.

Within our department, we provide an undergraduate program (B.Tech) that ignites the minds of young engineers. Our journey commenced in 2001 with a modest 60 seats, and today, we have expanded our capacity to 360 seats. Our faculty members are not just highly qualified but deeply passionate, relentlessly pushing the boundaries of technology to its fullest potential.

We comprehend that it's not just about academics; it's about the holistic development of individuals. This is why we prioritize providing you with invaluable industrial interactions and a curriculum that aligns with the latest industry trends. Whether you aspire to keep pace with the rapid advancements in the industry or lead the way, we stand ready to support you.

Your curriculum encompasses a range of captivating subjects, including Computer Programming, Networking, Data Structures and Algorithms, Database Management Systems, and the art of Software Engineering. Our state-of-the-art technology laboratories serve as your playground, where innovation and experimentation know no bounds.

I take immense pride in sharing that our department has an exceptional track record when it comes to campus recruitment. Prominent software companies such as Microsoft, Amazon, TCS, Headstrong, HCL, United Health Group, and others eagerly await the opportunity to welcome our graduates into their ranks. We are dedicated to ensuring that around 95% of our students find their path to success through campus placements.

So, as you embark on this journey with us, remember that the world of Computer Science and Engineering is teeming with boundless possibilities. I invite you to explore, dream, and innovate as you venture into the future.

Welcome to the Computer Science and Engineering Department, where your potential knows no limits.

Warm regards,

Prof. Kumud Saxena
Head - Computer Science and Engineering Department

Prof. Kumud Saxena

Head - Computer Science and Engineering Department

Elevating Excellence in Computer
Science & Engineering

","section1":"
  • Preparing students to apply their knowledge and varied skills as a competent technocrat.
  • Futuristic technical education and established as a department of excellence
  • Participation in National & International Technical conferences.
  • Faculty & Student participation in research and  projects.
  • State-of the art, Industry standard computing labs.
  • International Coding clubs & Communities
  • MOUs with lead industries for training.
  • Codetantra –Labs on codetantra
  • Industry aligned curriculum
  • Global certifications
  • Lab cum class concept
  • Workshops/Trainings

Training and Workshop conducted by Department of Computer Science & Engineering!

At the Department of CSE, we are committed to nurturing the next generation of tech innovators and professionals. With a rich history of excellence and a passion for technology, we are proud to offer a diverse range of workshops, training programs, and certification opportunities that equip our students with the skills they need to thrive in the ever-evolving world of IT.

Our Successful Workshops

Our workshops cover a wide spectrum of cutting-edge technologies and methodologies, ensuring that our students stay ahead in the tech race. Some of our successful workshops include:

C Programming

Master the foundations of programming with the C language, building a strong base for your coding journey.
Object-Oriented Techniques

Learn the principles of object-oriented programming, essential for creating scalable and efficient software.
Machine Learning

Dive deep into the world of artificial intelligence and machine learning, exploring data analysis, model building, and more.
Python & Advanced Python

Unleash the power of Python, from the basics to advanced topics. Our experts guide you through its applications in various domains.
Web Technology

Delving into the world of web development, our workshops cover everything from front-end to back-end, giving students a comprehensive understanding of web technology.

Data Science and Algorithms Training

Our training programs in Data Science and Algorithms (DSA) are designed to help students comprehend complex data structures, algorithms, and their practical applications. With these skills, you can tackle real-world challenges and contribute to the data-driven revolution.

Competitive Coding Mastery

For those who love the thrill of coding competitions, we offer competitive coding training. Hone your coding skills, improve your problem-solving abilities, and prepare for coding contests on a global stage.

Certification Programs

We understand the importance of industry-recognized certifications. To boost your career prospects, we provide certification programs in collaboration with top companies like Infosys Springboard, Amazon Web Services (AWS), and Google Cloud Platform (GCP). These certifications not only enhance your knowledge but also make you a preferred choice for leading employers.

Whether you're a student eager to kickstart your tech journey or a professional looking to upskill, the Department of Computer Science and Engineering is your gateway to a world of opportunities.

Join us, and let's embark on a journey towards technological excellence, innovation, and success. Your future in tech begins here!

Lab Cum Class Concept

At the Department of Computer Science and Engineering, we are committed to nurturing the next generation of tech innovators and professionals. With a rich history of excellence and a passion for technology, we are proud to offer a diverse range of workshops, training programs, and certification opportunities that equip our students with the skills they need to thrive in the ever-evolving world of IT.
